    <data key="d0">Avnet: Accelerating OEM&#x27;s with IoT and AI</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6E_Dg3YRil4</data>
    <data key="d2">Avnet's IoT Connect platform helps OEMs onboard devices and connect them to the cloud at scale. It separates the control plane (utilizing AWS Organizations, RDS, and API Gateway for customer provisioning) from the data plane. The data plane ingests telemetry via IoT Core, streaming to S3 and DynamoDB via Kinesis, and triggering Lambdas for business workflows. SageMaker and Bedrock run cloud-based ML model inferences and send predictions back to the devices.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive, control</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
